Adriano Domínguez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adriano_Dom%C3%ADnguez 0 Adriano Domínguez Fernández (4 January 1919– 9 May 2008) was a Spanish film and television actor. He appeared in 150 films between 1945 and 1994. Adriano_Domínguez_Fernández ( 4_January_1919 – 9_May_2008 ) was a_Spanish_film_and_television_actor . He appeared in 150_films between 1945_and_1994 .
